   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Microplastic in the Desert</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Awareness has been increasing on the effects that our society has on the Earth, notably there has been a push for understanding the quantity of microplastics we have in our oceans and categorising the plastics. However, other ecosystems on Earth are contaminated with microplastics. This study aims to investigate Microplastics in deserts and if microplastics are being transported by wind currents. Our first sampling campaign will be in the Utah dsert during a Mars simulation camp.</narrative>
  </description>
